Motor Boats Monthly - June 2014  UK

116 Pages | True PDF | English | 36 MB 


The UK's hardest-hitting and favourite motor boating magazine, Motor Boat Monthly is firmly focussed on practical motor cruising. With editorial coverage ranging from the booming RIB and sports boat markets right up to 40-foot cruisers and beyond, Motor Boat Monthly's comprehensive range of new and second-hand tests ensure that readers are always equipped with the very best buying information.
